        <p class="text-center f-light">Cyberbullying, sexting, and child abuse are online reality our children live in these days. Most parents cannot realize dangers of the Internet, since they simply had no chance to face anything alike in their childhood. Thus, it’s hard to understand what it means to be a teenager connected online 24/7. However, online danger do exists and sometimes it takes away kids’ lives.</p>
		
